00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:04.959
I did mean to steal.

00:01:05.359 --> 00:01:06.319
Please punish me.

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:14.719
Were you going to give it to your sister?

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:17.120
Don't worry.

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:18.359
We'll take good care of your sister.

00:01:19.159 --> 00:01:20.280
But first,

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:24.359
you need to take care of yourself.

00:01:25.159 --> 00:01:26.480
You must be hungry too.

00:01:26.480 --> 00:01:29.480
Eat.

00:01:29.480 --> 00:01:30.760
Once you're full,

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:32.359
you'll have the strength to care for your sister.

00:01:54.519 --> 00:01:55.319
Master Yi.

00:01:57.120 --> 00:01:57.879
Meiduo.

00:01:57.879 --> 00:01:58.680
What are you doing?

00:01:59.200 --> 00:01:59.640
What are you doing?

00:01:59.640 --> 00:01:59.840
Get up, quickly.

00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:00.280
Listen to me.

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:00.959
Master Yi.

00:02:03.359 --> 00:02:04.519
I sneaked over here.

00:02:05.159 --> 00:02:06.760
I want to thank you for saving my life.

00:02:08.120 --> 00:02:09.120
We are household serfs.

00:02:10.520 --> 00:02:12.120
What you Han people call slaves.

00:02:13.719 --> 00:02:14.560
From the moment we're born,

00:02:15.879 --> 00:02:18.240
our bodies and our lives

00:02:18.240 --> 00:02:19.479
are not our own.

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:24.199
We're bought like livestock,

00:02:24.199 --> 00:02:24.919
sold,

00:02:26.360 --> 00:02:27.319
and abused.

00:02:29.319 --> 00:02:32.360
We can only live like rats in a hole,

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:33.039
hiding

00:02:34.039 --> 00:02:34.840
and enduring.

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:39.120
You rescued us from hell.

00:02:41.919 --> 00:02:42.719
Meiduo.

00:02:44.039 --> 00:02:45.960
Meiduo has nothing to repay your kindness.

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.039
I can only...

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:56.560
I can only give myself to you.

00:02:57.919 --> 00:02:58.919
From now on,

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:00.960
Meiduo is yours.

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:04.159
You are Meiduo's master.

00:03:11.759 --> 00:03:12.560
Meiduo.

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:14.639
I didn't save you.

00:03:15.240 --> 00:03:17.319
You chose to bravely escape yourself.

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:19.719
You saved yourself.

00:03:22.960 --> 00:03:24.840
But since you've joined the Liberation Army,

00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:26.840
there are new rules now.

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:28.639
Come on.

00:03:28.639 --> 00:03:29.240
Get up first.

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:33.960
You must remember this,

00:03:34.719 --> 00:03:35.520
engrave it in your heart.

00:03:36.439 --> 00:03:37.240
First,

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:38.879
don't kneel to people casually.

00:03:39.319 --> 00:03:40.960
Everyone has a head on their shoulders.

00:03:41.439 --> 00:03:42.439
Everyone is equal.

00:03:43.080 --> 00:03:43.879
Second,

00:03:44.479 --> 00:03:45.960
You are not a yak,

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:47.120
not a silver coin,

00:03:47.479 --> 00:03:49.319
nor an object to be bought and sold.

00:03:49.879 --> 00:03:50.919
You are a person.

00:03:51.319 --> 00:03:52.439
You don't belong to anyone.

00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:55.159
You belong only to yourself.

00:03:56.280 --> 00:03:57.280
Do you understand?

00:03:59.159 --> 00:03:59.960
Master Yi.

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:02.759
I know you have a kind heart

00:04:03.319 --> 00:04:04.439
and won't accept me.

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.759
But Meiduo's heart has already acknowledged its master.

00:04:09.560 --> 00:04:10.599
Meiduo.

00:04:10.599 --> 00:04:11.319
Listen carefully.

00:04:11.919 --> 00:04:12.960
Don't call me Master Yi.

00:04:13.759 --> 00:04:15.039
You can call me Company Commander Yi,

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:17.279
or you can call me

00:04:17.279 --> 00:04:18.399
Brother Gao Yuan.

00:04:19.319 --> 00:04:20.480
It's not that I won't take you.

00:04:20.639 --> 00:04:22.879
It's that you have nothing to give.

00:04:22.879 --> 00:04:24.879
Those slave owners used whips and chains to tell you

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:26.319
that you are their property.

00:04:26.680 --> 00:04:27.680
But that's false.

00:04:27.879 --> 00:04:29.279
It's a man-eating lie.

00:04:30.519 --> 00:04:31.560
Now you are free.

00:04:32.279 --> 00:04:33.639
Your body,

00:04:33.639 --> 00:04:34.240
soul,

00:04:34.439 --> 00:04:34.959
will,

00:04:34.959 --> 00:04:36.000
and future...

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:36.959
From today onward,

00:04:37.079 --> 00:04:39.120
belong completely and only to yourself.

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:40.560
Do you understand?

00:04:45.480 --> 00:04:46.279
Come.

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:48.560
Look.

00:04:49.279 --> 00:04:50.360
That eagle in the sky,

00:04:50.959 --> 00:04:52.199
does it belong to any cloud?

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:55.319
It belongs only to its own wings.

00:04:55.920 --> 00:04:57.360
And Meiduo...

00:04:57.360 --> 00:04:58.920
also belongs only to Meiduo herself.

00:05:00.279 --> 00:05:01.079
Meiduo

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:03.959
belongs to Meiduo herself.

00:05:06.519 --> 00:05:07.800
At that moment,

00:05:07.800 --> 00:05:09.560
it was as if a crack opened in her heart,

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:11.519
and a light shone in.

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:13.680
Gesang Meiduo

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:15.560
belongs only to Gesang Meiduo herself.

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:17.279
Don't come any closer!

00:05:17.279 --> 00:05:18.439
Give me back my sister!

00:05:20.360 --> 00:05:21.120
Don't come over!

00:05:24.439 --> 00:05:25.160
Don't come over!

00:05:25.720 --> 00:05:25.959
Don't come over!

00:05:25.959 --> 00:05:26.160
Don't come over!

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:26.839
Don't be afraid.

00:05:26.839 --> 00:05:27.680
Let us explain.

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:29.279
Where is my sister?

00:05:29.639 --> 00:05:30.600
Deji!

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:31.639
Sister is here.

00:05:32.040 --> 00:05:33.240
Sister!

00:05:35.279 --> 00:05:36.079
What happened?

00:05:36.319 --> 00:05:37.439
Company Commander Yi.

00:05:37.439 --> 00:05:38.639
I went to give her the shoes.

00:05:38.720 --> 00:05:39.360
But then...

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:40.439
she saw me and ran.

00:05:40.680 --> 00:05:41.720
She ran, so I chased.

00:05:41.920 --> 00:05:42.839
She looked at me

00:05:42.839 --> 00:05:43.879
like I was a devil.

00:05:44.079 --> 00:05:45.079
Am I that scary?

00:05:45.079 --> 00:05:45.879
Sister!

00:05:46.439 --> 00:05:48.040
I thought you went to find food

00:05:48.079 --> 00:05:49.480
and they caught you.

00:05:49.480 --> 00:05:50.560
I was afraid they'd beat you,

00:05:50.560 --> 00:05:51.720
skin you alive.

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:53.399
I heard...

00:05:53.399 --> 00:05:54.639
I heard many people say

00:05:54.639 --> 00:05:56.120
the Red Han people are Red Devils.

00:05:56.319 --> 00:05:57.759
They eat people without spitting out the bones.

00:05:58.720 --> 00:05:59.600
Red Devils?

00:05:59.600 --> 00:06:01.560
Would they give us tsampa to eat?

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:02.879
Give us milk to drink,

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:04.759
and new shoes to wear?

00:06:05.879 --> 00:06:06.759
Do you remember,

00:06:06.839 --> 00:06:09.040
when we worked at Balu Manor,

00:06:09.560 --> 00:06:12.480
those girls in uniforms who were singing?

00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:13.560
Mm-hmm.

00:06:14.959 --> 00:06:15.839
Sister.

00:06:15.839 --> 00:06:18.040
Then they are the same as those girls.

00:06:18.040 --> 00:06:18.959
They are all...

00:06:19.079 --> 00:06:20.560
We are all Liberation Army soldiers.

00:06:20.759 --> 00:06:22.120
Not man-eating Red Devils.

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:24.959
But you look so fierce,

00:06:25.160 --> 00:06:26.480
not like a good person.

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:26.959
I...

00:06:26.959 --> 00:06:28.959
Ha ha ha!

00:06:28.959 --> 00:06:30.360
What are you laughing at? Get back to work!

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:31.959
Go on!

00:06:51.759 --> 00:06:52.560
How are you?

00:06:52.680 --> 00:06:54.319
Feeling better?

00:06:55.959 --> 00:06:56.959
Doctor Li.

00:06:56.959 --> 00:06:57.439
Battalion Commander.

00:06:57.439 --> 00:06:59.079
That soldier fainted.

00:06:59.079 --> 00:06:59.879
Let's go check on him.

00:06:59.879 --> 00:07:00.680
Okay.

00:07:05.160 --> 00:07:05.959
Hey.

00:07:07.240 --> 00:07:08.319
Deji.

00:07:08.319 --> 00:07:09.120
What are you doing here?

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:09.959
Brother Gao Yuan.

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:11.920
Ah.

00:07:12.519 --> 00:07:13.319
Please, sit.

00:07:13.519 --> 00:07:14.319
I'll sit.

00:07:19.279 --> 00:07:20.079
You are...

00:07:21.439 --> 00:07:22.360
Let me give you an injection.

00:07:22.360 --> 00:07:22.920
Hold on.

00:07:24.319 --> 00:07:25.399
How many days have you been

00:07:25.399 --> 00:07:26.319
learning from Doctor Li?

00:07:26.319 --> 00:07:27.120
Hmm.

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:29.519
I've practiced many times.

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:32.480
Just one shot.

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:33.920
Let me try.

00:07:34.879 --> 00:07:36.079
Go learn from Doctor Li for a few more days,

00:07:36.079 --> 00:07:37.000
then you can inject me.

00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:41.040
Just one shot.

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:41.839
Brother Gao Yuan.

00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:42.519
How about this.

00:07:42.519 --> 00:07:44.800
I'll find Zhuzi for you

00:07:44.800 --> 00:07:45.560
to practice on.

00:07:46.399 --> 00:07:46.800
No, no.

00:07:47.199 --> 00:07:47.519
Don't.

00:07:47.519 --> 00:07:48.040
Zhuzi!

00:07:48.480 --> 00:07:49.279
Zhuzi!

00:07:49.319 --> 00:07:50.160
Come here, quick!

00:07:50.639 --> 00:07:51.279
Uh...

00:07:51.279 --> 00:07:52.439
Let Comrade Deji

00:07:52.439 --> 00:07:53.439
give you a couple of shots.

00:07:53.759 --> 00:07:55.240
I'm not sick, why would you inject me?

00:07:57.519 --> 00:07:58.560
Then call, call, call Sun Chen.

00:07:59.120 --> 00:07:59.879
I'll inject you.

00:07:59.879 --> 00:08:00.319
Sun Chen!

00:08:00.319 --> 00:08:00.680
I'll inject you.

00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:01.480
Sun Chen!

00:08:01.959 --> 00:08:02.720
Where's Sun Chen?

00:08:02.959 --> 00:08:04.680
I'll inject you, Brother Gao Yuan.

00:08:14.079 --> 00:08:14.959
Let's go.

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:18.600
Zhuzi!

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:19.920
Hurry up!

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:20.560
Don't slack off.

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:21.839
Brother Gao Yuan.

00:08:22.639 --> 00:08:23.439
You've worked hard.

00:08:23.439 --> 00:08:24.240
Have some water.

00:08:35.120 --> 00:08:35.919
Miss Meiduo.

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:36.960
Thank you.

00:08:37.759 --> 00:08:38.879
The weather is too hot.

00:08:38.960 --> 00:08:40.080
Let me wipe your sweat.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:40.879
Ah.

00:08:41.440 --> 00:08:42.080
No, no need.

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:43.120
I can do it myself.

00:08:44.559 --> 00:08:46.159
Did I do something wrong?

00:08:47.320 --> 00:08:49.080
No, no, not at all.

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:52.919
Your face is so red.

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:54.759
Why are you so hot?

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:57.159
This weather, I tell you...

00:08:57.159 --> 00:08:59.159
If only it would rain.

00:09:02.320 --> 00:09:03.720
Yeah, that's true.

00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:04.960
It's too hot.

00:09:05.320 --> 00:09:06.159
Uh...

00:09:06.559 --> 00:09:07.360
Miss Meiduo.

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:09.559
Let me show you something fun.

00:09:10.879 --> 00:09:11.840
Look.

00:09:11.840 --> 00:09:12.559
This is called

00:09:12.559 --> 00:09:13.360
a harmonica.

00:09:13.720 --> 00:09:14.519
Don't let its size fool you.

00:09:14.679 --> 00:09:16.240
It can play many different tunes.

00:09:16.840 --> 00:09:17.399
Really?

00:09:17.399 --> 00:09:18.039
Ah.

00:09:18.559 --> 00:09:19.360
I'll play it for you.

00:09:20.759 --> 00:09:21.559
Okay.

00:09:21.840 --> 00:09:22.639
Let's go.

00:09:43.039 --> 00:09:44.159
Brother Gao Yuan

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:46.639
was playing an instrument I'd never seen before.

00:09:46.919 --> 00:09:48.519
The melody was also unfamiliar.

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:50.440
But those notes,

00:09:50.440 --> 00:09:51.679
falling into my ears,

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:53.039
were like a key

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:55.960
suddenly unlocking the cage that had trapped me all my life.

00:09:56.679 --> 00:09:58.799
I was still standing on this plateau,

00:09:59.200 --> 00:10:01.559
yet it felt like I had stepped into another world.

00:10:04.039 --> 00:10:04.840
Sister.

00:10:05.720 --> 00:10:07.159
The Liberation Army really is good.

00:10:07.159 --> 00:10:08.879
Everyone treats me very well.

00:10:08.879 --> 00:10:10.440
They give me lots of candy.

00:10:12.039 --> 00:10:12.840
Sister.

00:10:13.320 --> 00:10:14.960
I want to follow Doctor Li Yuling

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:15.759
and learn how to give injections.

00:10:16.879 --> 00:10:17.960
Of course.

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:19.000
Whatever you want to do,

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:20.000
your sister supports you.

00:10:21.039 --> 00:10:22.639
But our little Deji,

00:10:22.639 --> 00:10:23.639
your head is a bit slow.

00:10:23.639 --> 00:10:25.480
You'll have to study hard.

00:10:26.559 --> 00:10:27.840
Deji is not slow!

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:30.440
I'll go find Doctor Li right now

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:31.360
to learn injections.

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:31.720
Hmph!

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:37.480
Brother Gao Yuan.

00:10:37.480 --> 00:10:38.039
Meiduo.

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:39.720
I have good news for you.

00:10:39.919 --> 00:10:41.000
The Xizang Work Committee

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:42.559
and the Preparatory Committee for the Autonomous Region

00:10:42.559 --> 00:10:44.840
have decided to select a group of outstanding Tibetan youth

00:10:44.840 --> 00:10:45.960
to work in various units.

00:10:46.360 --> 00:10:47.159
You and Deji

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:48.279
both have the opportunity

00:10:48.279 --> 00:10:49.480
to enter the Cadre School for study.

00:10:52.039 --> 00:10:53.919
Will we still get to see you if we go?

00:10:54.639 --> 00:10:55.440
Yes.

00:10:56.120 --> 00:10:57.039
I'll have the chance

00:10:57.039 --> 00:10:58.080
to visit you.

00:11:06.279 --> 00:11:07.480
This is a small token of my appreciation.

00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:08.919
For you.

00:11:11.720 --> 00:11:12.519
Alright then.

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:14.000
Thank you, sir.

00:11:16.080 --> 00:11:16.679
Let me teach you.

00:11:16.679 --> 00:11:17.039
Come here.

00:11:17.519 --> 00:11:18.639
Upper arm leads the forearm.

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:20.360
Start from the chest.

00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:20.879
Try it.

00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:23.519
Mm-hmm.

00:11:23.519 --> 00:11:24.320
That's right.